    "description": "<p>MSE Engineering and Management Consultants was established on 1st January 1983; the Principals are Alec Chew Khek Han and John Lim Kheng Hock. Both partners have more than four decade of practical experience in the administration of various civil and structural engineering works. Previous projects undertaken by the partners range from flyovers, water supply schemes, low cost housing, hotels, hospitals, churches, high rise condominiums, airport buildings, institutional and commercial buildings, and industrial complexes. The firm also offers management services to contractors undertaking government projects. Since 200, a consortium of association has been formed with world renowned engineer Dr. Alfred Yee of Precast Design Consultants who now shares an office with us to serve a wider spectrum of clientele requiring varied engineering consultation and management. The ultimate aim is to give excellence of service to our clientele.</p>",
